{"tid":2491541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇外國新聞建議睇Sky News Australia","createTime":"2021-04-16T11:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T13:10:01.000Z","uid":178187,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f7ff69d3a8a8fe51264cf75ec53f7a53df0048c4","tid":2491541,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T11:45:11.000Z","msg":"基本上大部份香港人識既英美媒體例如BBC CNN NBC ABC Guardian Sky News ITV Channel 4都係偏左至左膠。係抹黑trump trump同宣傳黑人命貴上不遺餘力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但呢個Sky News Australia 不得止直線屌鳩中國，仲屌埋Black Lives Matter, Biden 同埋充斥住西方社會既左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好難得集兩家大成，連英國自己Sky News都係不斷洗腦植入左膠思想。我都唔明點解澳洲個邊咁大膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而且香港蘋果啲國際新聞都係偏左膠路線(另加係咁植入大陸字眼洗你腦)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以好少有媒體可以做到咁好。建議大家訂閱佢地YouTube channel 支持下。當練下聽下英文都好，而且佢哋澳洲口音未至於重到聽唔明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtube.com/user/SkyNewsAustralia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fuser%2FSkyNewsAustralia&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=35168dfd\" target=\"_blank\">youtube.com/user/SkyNewsAustralia</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 關於中國既新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nworld war xi inside china's cold war with the west<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ri4NBy_PrGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRi4NBy_PrGI&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=3adc57d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ri4NBy_PrGI</a><br />\n<br />\nchina just sent a chilling message to the rest of the world<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xUsntuFS3EY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxUsntuFS3EY&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=12e97c22\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xUsntuFS3EY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now &lsquo;game on&rsquo; between Beijing and the west <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FoJwA_-VGvU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFoJwA_-VGvU&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=cb46a5c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FoJwA_-VGvU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe tensions between Taiwan and China are dangerous and should be seen as such <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CAhWcCiTD-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCAhWcCiTD-g&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=a2c02e45\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CAhWcCiTD-g</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關於Biden <br />\n<br />\nWe may soon be in grave danger from China with Biden in charge: Bolt<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PErTNo2XYxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPErTNo2XYxU&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=58239175\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PErTNo2XYxU</a><br />\n<br />\nLaptop evidence strongly indicates Joe Biden is compromised on China <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g4gXUp-kH4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg4gXUp-kH4M&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=12c08dfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g4gXUp-kH4M</a><br />\n<br />\nThe leader of the western world is cognitively deficient <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/V43JwzZ_ALs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FV43JwzZ_ALs&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=97973e85\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/V43JwzZ_ALs</a>"},{"pid":"47dbc1fdefc071c0782bb288ecf33daebcd23951","tid":2491541,"uid":178187,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T11:46:59.000Z","msg":"仲有好多好多冇擺上嚟，大家去YouTube search Sky News Australia 支持下"},{"pid":"b38a3fe675bb15db9b718b312f11eeaeed3fb871","tid":2491541,"uid":361380,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆"},{"pid":"1823f624b39b10716d25e5bdf48acad7ea3b3638","tid":2491541,"u